# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# GreenPath AI — Environment Variables
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# No environment variables are REQUIRED to run this project.
# The scoring engine is fully rule-based (no external AI API calls).
#
# Optional: If you integrate a live Gemini / OpenAI API in future:
# GEMINI_API_KEY=your_key_here
#
# Copy this file to .env.local for local development:
#   cp .env.example .env.local
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
